author: Orion Rummler
title: In photos: Americans rally in more states to protest coronavirus social distancing
description: Protesters gathered at state capitols in Washington and in Colorado Sunday to oppose the state closures of businesses and schools designed to slow the spread of the coronavirus by enforcing social distancing. Similar protests were staged in California, Texas …
